  <lyrics>[V1]
 Calvariokama noqarayku rerqa,
 Señor Jesús noqarayku.
 Calvariokama noqarayku rerqa,
 Salvasqaña kani.
 
[C]
 Juchasapapis noqa kashaspa, Pay
 /Juchayta qhechuwan cruzpi wañuspa./
 
[V2]
 Pay cielokamapis noqarayku rin,
 Señor Jesús, noqarayku.
 Pay cielokamapis noqarayku rin
 Pay mañapushawan.
 
</lyrics></song>